  "body": "*Title*: Expose Live Circuit Breaker State\r\n\r\n*Description*: Currently, Envoy doesn't expose the \"live\" Circuit Breaker state (open/closed), and it'd be useful to export that (probably via [stats](https://www.envoyproxy.io/docs/envoy/latest/configuration/cluster_manager/cluster_stats#config-cluster-manager-cluster-stats)).\r\n\r\n*Relevant Links*:\r\nistio/istio#8902\r\nhttps://issues.jboss.org/browse/KIALI-470?_sscc=t\r\nhttps://groups.google.com/forum/#!msg/istio-users/GMaLai6aTa4/ymfDMu8TCQAJ;context-place=forum/istio-users",
